{"tid":1063583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美大學生放春假擠「淫島」　揉奶射顏春色無邊","createTime":"2019-03-16T01:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T06:40:07.000Z","uid":72009,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d9f2abef718653292f120b0b83926f1c4547c6","tid":1063583,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:17:09.000Z","msg":"3月份是美國各級學校的春假高峰，春假的娛樂內容更是高潮不斷，海灘邊聚集許多男男女女，大家隨著潮水海風嗨爆升天。<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，這個位在德州墨西哥灣的南帕瑞島(South Padre Island)，平時只有5000人口，到只要到了春假，就會湧進10萬名大學生來狂歡，讓寧靜的小島頓時間成為「淫島」。現場可以看到不少狂歡派對，而且玩很大，包括揉奶、水槍射顏、老漢推車等各種遊戲，全部登場，當然少不了酗酒、嗑藥等問題，相信也發生不少撿屍事件。<br />\n這也讓當地警方傷透腦筋，30歲警長羅薩斯(Jose De La Rosas)就說，每到3月春假就是他們警方最忙碌的時候，因為他的轄區不大，警力有限，而他的小小團隊卻要派到南帕瑞島，應付龐大的狂歡人潮與秩序。不僅如此，他們的警力還要處理美墨邊境問題，包括走私、販毒、人口販賣等，壓力相當大。<br />\n但對商家來說，春假卻是賺錢的好時機，因為有龐大的狂歡人潮，絕對少不了酒的助興。據統計，光是在3~4月期間，大學生在南帕瑞島買酒就花了總共310萬美元(約新台幣9300萬元)，更為南帕瑞島帶來3390萬美元(約新台幣10億元)的收入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190316/1534235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190316%2F1534235&d=hEl8YzVD%2FOsYsQiwoICJnMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=4fdbf093\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190316%2F1534235&h=88d4ccc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190316/1534235</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190316/640_efaea84e1935a0efab8f8f7c726366e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190316%2F640_efaea84e1935a0efab8f8f7c726366e9.jpg&h=21dcdfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190316/640_59b2b62c62ca505d33e391b58fb88878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190316%2F640_59b2b62c62ca505d33e391b58fb88878.jpg&h=79c31d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190316/640_1d6f4efb4e04b51b712a998a1f4b7e83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190316%2F640_1d6f4efb4e04b51b712a998a1f4b7e83.jpg&h=5500e1ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190316/640_c3ad3ddf9442ab2bad978f34f33f2306.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190316%2F640_c3ad3ddf9442ab2bad978f34f33f2306.jpg&h=1436b3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190316/640_0864c036718090f81c5214a0a4aacaa0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190316%2F640_0864c036718090f81c5214a0a4aacaa0.jpg&h=2813cab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190316/640_5ac6045bcaf092d546706ab1f4d62f26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190316%2F640_5ac6045bcaf092d546706ab1f4d62f26.jpg&h=00ec8429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肉便器太多"},{"pid":"4e3bfb7d86fe21b4f64e671645457c184bec0d33","tid":1063583,"uid":40470,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:19:18.000Z","msg":"毒撚又係行埋一邊睇人玩一邊打飛機"},{"pid":"b2f4a53c024d5d709b59606bd6b40083fc66dd35","tid":1063583,"uid":177288,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:20:02.000Z","msg":"想去"},{"pid":"4ad13dfef7025a30b7ae83a04c2e4acab5ad87e6","tid":1063583,"uid":33733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"有冇更多更多更多圖"},{"pid":"99dfa07aa2d8f3cdf66df48d3fe09ef6a73774e6","tid":1063583,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b2f4a53c024d5d709b59606bd6b40083fc66dd35","tid":1063583,"uid":177288,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-1